Hunters are very strong and highly mobile fighters.  Prioritizing agility and 
crit, hunters deal a large amount of damage while being able to kite enemies.  
Gear choices often trade between stam and agility depending on the group makeup 
and playstyle.  Pets are chosen based on their raid buffs and CC ability, and BM 
hunters can tame exotic pets.  The most difficult part of creating a hunter is 
that the best scope (Flintlocke’s Woodchucker) requires the player to have a 
level 80 hunter on the same account.  Note that Flintlocke’s Woodchucker is not 
allowed in competitive arenas, but is allowed in WSG. 

